title: Calliostoma aporia
text:
Calliostoma aporia is a <a href="species">species</a> of <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a marine <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a> in the <a href="family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Calliostomatidae">Calliostomatidae</a>.
Distribution.
This marine species occurs off the <a href="Solomon%20Islands">Solomon Islands</a>.
